      Suppresses INFO/DEBUG logs from framework unless something breaks.
      Logs to both console and file. Additivity disabled to prevent bubbling.

    - org.testng.internal â†’ Level: WARN
      Silences verbose internal TestNG logs (e.g., method sorting, graph creation).
